item.description:
I recently bought an SSL certificate from Comodo, and when I got my certificate I also received two intermediate certificates&hellip;
The problem came when trying to import the two intermediate certificates&hellip; on the Synology DSM 5.0 firmware, there&rsquo;s only one field for the intermediate certificates&hellip;

So how did I get both certificates into the one file? It&rsquo;s actually really simple - I combined the two certificates into a single, .
